Revision 4
+ Config file can be specified at the command line with -c. Default is to search for sephiabot.cfg in the current directory.
+ Shows usage if started with --help.
+ Log directory is read from the config file. Logs are buffered until the config file can be opened.
+ Defaults are now present for some values if not specified in the config file.
! Logs are appended to syslog.txt instead of rewriting.
! Changed default sephiabot.cfg
! Changed spaces to 4-character tabs.
! Minor bugfixes
